<br>
Create a command called /cityraid.<br>
When the leader of the raid force types in this command, it would generate a dialogue box, like that for a rez, for everyone in the zone. The box would say &quot;&lt;character name&gt; has declared an attack on &lt;city zone&gt;, do you wish to participate in this PVP event?&quot;. <br>
<br>
If you click yes, you're name turns red and you are on pvp status until either the agressors /endcity raid, or you leave the zone.<br>
<br>
This option would allow defenders of their home towns to fight against any agressors, without griefing the assault force.<br>
<br>
Those who don't wish to go pvp can simply click NO and go about their business, or watch the carnage, whichever suits their needs. That way any newbies in the area wont get squashed by the attacking highlevels.<br>
<br>
Just a thought.<br>
-Traxxus <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=castinareleas@firionavie>CastinarEleas</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 261<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(12/17/02 1:55:18 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3321.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: /Cityraid: an idea for SOE</span><hr size=1> Hmm... .I like it!  (Considers pseudocode required to activate it.... hmm...doesn't sound too difficult... most of the elements are there already... asuming PvP status is a boolean flag that can be switched off...) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=cieloinfierno>Cielo Infierno</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bare is beautiful Mod!<br>Apep, I have been naughty<br>I need a spanking.<br>The Blankie Girl</span><br>  Posts: 386<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(12/17/02 2:00:56 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3321.topic&index=2>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: /Cityraid: an idea for SOE</span><hr size=1> *drools on herself at the thought* Mmm.... /cityraid *drools some more* <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=288664"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.e2-online.net/eqsigs/sig_cielo.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--